!Entity "User"
The predefined entity [[User]] is available at any time and provides these attributes:

<ul><li>[text {"input"}]
The most recent user input. Other than the parameters of the current action this one contains the whole command the user typed in.
</li><li>[bool {"canceled"}]
[[True]] if the user pressed escape during the most recent %ask% or %wait% request.
</li><li>[number {"actions"}]
The number of actions the user has performed in this game session.
</li></ul>
